io.amelia.data

Interface KeyValueTypesTrait<ExceptionClass extends ApplicationException.Error>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConfigData, Parcel, UserContext

    public interface KeyValueTypesTrait<ExceptionClass extends ApplicationException.Error>
    Provides common methods for converting an unknown value to (and from) Object using the Java 8 Optional feature.

    These types include: Boolean Color Double Enum Integer Long String File List Class
